<div class="about-page">
  <h1>About Amazonia Pet Supplies</h1>
  <p>Welcome to Amazonia Pet Supplies, your number one source for all things pet-related. We're dedicated to providing you the very best of pet supplies, with an emphasis on quality, customer service, and uniqueness inspired by the beautiful fauna of Brazil.</p>

  <h2>Our Story</h2>
  <p>Founded in 2023, Amazonia Pet Supplies has come a long way from its beginnings in a small home office. When we first started out, our passion for eco-friendly, high-quality pet products drove us to start our own business.</p>

  <h2>Our Mission</h2>
  <p>Our mission is to bring the vibrant and rich biodiversity of Brazil into the homes of pet lovers everywhere. We believe pets are family, and they deserve the very best. That's why we source only the highest quality products that are safe, sustainable, and inspired by the Amazonian wildlife.</p>

